alisa de Carolis, Francesco Cilluffo, Marcello Lippi, Margherita Rotondi, Michele Ricciarini, Opera lirica, Pietro Mascagni, Rudy Park, Taisiya Ermolaeva, Valerio Alfieri"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/0e62e7fc5162665b3df65e036eafc43e" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Voci-3-130x200.jpg" width="65" height="100" alt="Gabriele Verdinelli" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Gabriele Verdinelli"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/gabriele-verdinelli/">View all articles by Gabriele Verdinelli</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/opera-de-toulonnorma/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Opra de Toulon:&#8221;Norma&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/gaetano-despinosa-dirige-bruckner-a-torino/" rel="next">Gaetano dEspinosa dirige Bruckner a Torino <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 1 comment</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-18611"> <article id="comment-18611" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/e5fedce22ea6f0b897ed7fecc1afdc35?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">Fabrizio</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/sassaricavalleria-rusticana/#comment-18611"><time datetime="2013-10-29T16:12:37+00:00">29 ottobre 2013 at 16:12</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Marcel Proust, nel suo celeberrimo lavoro &#8220;alla ricerca del tempo perduto&#8221;, nel libro &#8220;all&#8217;ombra delle Fanciulle in fiore&#8221;, rimane sorpreso che la su amata Albertine, sensibile e colta conoscitrice dell&#8217;arte pittorica grazie anche all&#8217;amicizia col pittore Elstir, non dimostri altrettanta cultura musicale raffinata insistendo a voler partecipare alla rappresentazione di &#8220;Cavalleria Rusticana&#8221; in piazza&#8230;</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li></ol><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2013/10/sassaricavalleria-rusticana/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sar pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea>